PeeDee Belemnite (VPDB) standard and for 15N = |XML| xmlLoc_0 xmlBold_no xmlItalic_no xmlFontSize_smaller xmlPic_no xmlTable_no xmlBullet_no bi_xmlSFBIA_new bi_xmlPara_new
0.0%o versus air nitrogen. The first anaylsis (sealed- |XML| xmlLoc_0 xmlBold_no xmlItalic_no xmlFontSize_smaller xmlPic_no xmlTable_no xmlBullet_no bi_xmlSFBIA_continue bi_xmlPara_continue
tube combustion with subsequent measurement on a |XML| xmlLoc_0 xmlBold_no xmlItalic_no xmlFontSize_smaller xmlPic_no xmlTable_no xmlBullet_no bi_xmlSFBIA_continue bi_xmlPara_continue
