ducibility of ± 0.08%o for organic standards. The |XML| xmlLoc_0 xmlBold_no xmlItalic_no xmlFontSize_smaller xmlPic_no xmlTable_no xmlBullet_no bi_xmlSFBIA_continue bi_xmlPara_continue
second analysis [elemental analyzer–continuous-flow |XML| xmlLoc_0 xmlBold_no xmlItalic_no xmlFontSize_smaller xmlPic_no xmlTable_no xmlBullet_no bi_xmlSFBIA_continue bi_xmlPara_continue
isotope ratio mass spectrometry (EA/CFIRMS)] used a |XML| xmlLoc_0 xmlBold_no xmlItalic_no xmlFontSize_smaller xmlPic_no xmlTable_no xmlBullet_no bi_xmlSFBIA_continue bi_xmlPara_continue
Carlo Erba NC2500 interfaced through a Finnigan |XML| xmlLoc_0 xmlBold_no xmlItalic_no xmlFontSize_smaller xmlPic_no xmlTable_no xmlBullet_no bi_xmlSFBIA_continue bi_xmlPara_continue
