Each of the 12,127 samples typed carried |XML| xmlLoc_3 xmlBold_no xmlItalic_no xmlFontSize_common xmlPic_no xmlTable_no xmlBullet_no bi_xmlSFBIA_continue bi_xmlPara_new
one of the three polymorphisms (YAP+, |XML| xmlLoc_3 xmlBold_no xmlItalic_no xmlFontSize_common xmlPic_no xmlTable_no xmlBullet_no bi_xmlSFBIA_continue bi_xmlPara_continue
